			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Mage Robe Quest</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=33323"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:emmit97@earthlink.net">Lyan</a> | 
		                        1/3/2000 3:58:23 AM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">OK, this is for all you mages out there.  I am pretty sure we were jipped in this quest.  I have found 2 out of the 3 pieces need for the Robe. I have the Ice Goblin Skin and the cloak off the fairy guard but i cannot find the fire goblin skin anywhere....AND ITS NOT IN SOL A OR ANYWHERE IN LAVA.  I have had friends spend days on end in SOL A killed every goblin over and over again and didnt see one sign of the skin.  but when they went to perma for the ice goblin skin it took us a whole 5 mins to get.  If you have any info on where to get the fire goblin skin please post it im dieing to get this darn robe.
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
